regions.data-sovereignty-title: Mana Motuhake Raraunga me te Motuhake Rohe
regions.data-sovereignty-description: Ka noho ō raraunga i tō rohe i kōwhiria e koe anake, ā, kāore e tukuna ki ngā rohe kē
regions.separate-environments-explanation: Ka mahi ia rohe hei taiao motuhake tino me ōna ake hanganga, kī whakamuhumuhu, me te rokiroki raraunga
regions.no-data-transfer-policy: Kei a mātou tētahi kaupapa here mārō: kāore e tukuna ngā raraunga kiritaki i waenga i ngā rohe i raro i ngā āhuatanga katoa
regions.switching-creates-new-account: Nui te take: Ko te huri ki tētahi rohe kē ka hanga i tētahi pūkete hou. Ka noho ō raraunga i tō rohe taketake.
regions.explore-other-regions: Tūhuratia ngā rohe kē e wātea ana
regions.why-it-matters: He Aha Te Take o te Mana Motuhake Raraunga
regions.trust-description: Mōhio tika ki te wāhi e noho ana ō raraunga me ngā ture e whakahaere ana i tōna tiaki.
regions.privacy-description: Whakaū ka whakahaerea ō mōhiohio whaiaro e ai ki ngā ture me ngā ture matatapu o tō whenua, hei ārai i te urunga kore mana, te kino whakamahi rānei.
regions.compliance-description: Whakatutuki i ngā whakaritenga tiaki raraunga rohe pērā i GDPR, HIPAA, CCPA, me ētahi atu
regions.performance-description: Ko ngā raraunga kua rokirokihia tata ki a koe, ka iti ake te wā takaroa, ka pai ake te mahi.
